  "body": "## What's Changed\r\nWe updated dd-trace-js from v5.105.0 to v5.109.0\r\nFull Changelogs:\r\n- dd-trace https://github.com/DataDog/dd-trace-js/compare/v5.105.0...v5.109.0\r\n- datadog-lambda-js https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-js/compare/v12.139.0...v12.140.0\r\n\r\n>[!IMPORTANT]\r\n> This version imports `dd-trace-js` [v5.109.0](https://github.com/DataDog/dd-trace-js/releases/tag/v5.109.0)\r\n\r\n```yml\r\n# AWS Commercial\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Node18-x:140\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Node20-x:140\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Node22-x:140\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Node24-x:140\r\n\r\n# AWS GovCloud\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Node18-x:140\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Node20-x:140\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Node22-x:140\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Node24-x:140\r\n\r\nACCOUNT =\r\n002406178527 for us1 environment\r\n486696501492 for us2 environment\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n"
